$ SQL Server T-SQL: error handling

  The → development/databases/SQL-Server/T-SQL/statements/throw[`throw`] statement

  In a `catch` block, the → development/databases/SQL-Server/T-SQL/error-handling/severity-level can be determined with
  → development/databases/SQL-Server/T-SQL/statements/catch/error_severity[`error_severity()`].

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/T-SQL/raiserror[`raisError()`]

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/administration/schemas/sys/objects/views/sysmessages[`sys.sysmessages`]
